            "notes": "The deck focuses on utilizing Grist, The Hunger Tide as the commander to create a fast and aggressive playstyle. The main strategy revolves around utilizing a mix of ramp creatures like Arbor Elf, Birds of Paradise, and Elvish Mystic to accelerate mana production and quickly cast powerful threats like Primeval Titan and Vengevine. The deck also includes disruption like Thoughtseize and Fatal Push to control the board and disrupt the opponent's strategy. Additionally, the deck features graveyard recursion with cards like Animate Dead and Eternal Witness to continually bring back threats. By overwhelming the opponent with early threats and disrupting their game plan, the deck aims to quickly take control of the game and secure a victory."
